  <section>
    <h2>Relief for Itchy, Uncomfortable Pets</h2>
    <p>
      If your dog won't stop scratching or your cat keeps getting ear infections, allergies could be the cause. Pet allergies are one of the most common — and most frustrating — conditions we see, and they rarely resolve on their own. At Healthy Paws Animal Hospital in Lake in the Hills, IL, we take a methodical approach to <strong>diagnosing the root cause</strong> of your pet's symptoms and building a treatment plan that actually works.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our team has earned a reputation for helping pets with chronic skin and allergy issues. We know how exhausting it is to watch your pet suffer through constant itching, and we're here to get them comfortable again — using the latest treatments in a <strong>gentle, low-stress</strong> environment that keeps stress low during every visit.
    </p>
